text: Simba António Castelo (born November 23, 1994, Luanda, Angola), better known by his stage name Preto Hendrik, is an African musician, of Angolan nationality, native of Luanda, member of LBA Music. began his artistic career in the year 2016, with music named "Encher a Cara", and "Fácil" with group of musicians LBA Musc in 2016. == Discography == === Music === Year With LBA Music 2016 "Encher a Cara", "Fácil" ==References== ==Other websites== * Category:Angolan people Category:1994 births Category:Living people
